@node Offline "Adding Faqs off line."

Its simple really but you must do it right otherwise 
I don't know what TeaBot will do.

Below is a sample FaqList Database file
    
                                       <--- Database starts with a blank line
@{"@" LINK @}Bots                      <--- This is a faq drawer all drawers start with a @
Ilona The better bot =)                <--- Ilona is the faq topic and the rest is the faq
                                       <--- Blank line seperates Faq Drawers
@{"@" LINK @}Users                     <--- Another drawer (starts with a @)
Dibbs the magic hair dude              <--- Guess
Nikki extremely damn cute floridian :) <--- Guess
				

		
Easy eh ! Just follow those rules and you'll have no problems. 
You'll find the faqlist in s: enjoy yourself :)


@{" Back to Index " LINK Main}
@endnode

